Program can be run from the Driver class. Once run, we will get the below input: 

================================================
 1.   Who is the ruler of Southeros?
 2.   Allies of King Shan? 
 3.   Messages to kingdoms from King Shan
 4.   Exit 
================================================

Type 1 and hit enter to see  : Who is the ruler of Southeros?
Type 2 and hit enter to see  : Allies of King Shan 
Type 3 and hit enter to send encrypted messages to kingdoms  : Messages to kingdoms from King Shan
		Enter message and hit enter
		Continue to [3] -> [Enter] -> [Send Message] till you want to send message
		
Type 4 to exit from the program